{"tid":2250584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女蒲麻雀館熱潮貪方便隨時打得贏錢即走｜壹週刊｜","createTime":"2020-10-20T08:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T11:02:18.000Z","uid":325881,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c061d6d657d61777533de5b2a0148995717d7859","tid":2250584,"uid":325881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_763115_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_763115_0&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYESWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=3cb081c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_763115_0&h=3899b0cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_763115_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北美通訊）麻雀館，又稱「竹館」，由於以前麻雀乃竹製成，所以去麻雀館打牌俗稱「刮竹」，本是香港老一輩的耍樂。麻雀館一般給人的感覺，都是帶點神秘感，不少人對內裏的印象或許還停留在九十年代，港產江湖片中的講數場面，以為麻雀館滿佈惡人，龍蛇混集、刀光劍影；又或者會認為，進出麻雀館的多為大叔大嬸。想不到，近年竟然多了一群二十多歲的年輕港女光顧，彷彿令麻雀館添加了一點青春氣息，而她們鍾情於麻雀館的原因亦各有不同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘇淼淼，經營著美妝生意，亦是在朋友提議下，十八歲第一次踏足麻雀館：「只記得當時被一些阿伯揶揄，因為我打牌一定不夠他們熟練，那時剛剛學懂打牌，也是胡亂打，他們起初會責備我。」她自言，自己進竹館純粹為了消磨時間。"},{"pid":"f4a8a68518eda19d4f32ff4689a1aad8352728c0","tid":2250584,"uid":321977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"蘇淼淼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4c6123e68c6b3704bf051820d58113ca690f74","tid":2250584,"uid":122134,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"都係啲MK妹姐"},{"pid":"cefb5e99c9eda359dd8db55c93c38f9c02df7f2a","tid":2250584,"uid":71237,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:07:24.000Z","msg":"又係蘇淼淼"},{"pid":"8758d6e0c3e54667969c2e430c7760b1aff42d77","tid":2250584,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"割禾青<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858331e66234ca2c912888d1fa7803c938f69ae8","